Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:04.61,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Encounters are mysterious!\NBut the world is even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:06.74,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:10.05,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Today is a weather lady!\NPager logic will clear the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.72,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.58,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:16.22,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
